106 0 obj
<< /Length 2675 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: Is the Mediterranean diet good for weight loss?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Yes. While not a 'diet' in the restrictive sense, the Mediterranean pattern naturally) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (promotes healthy weight through whole foods, healthy fats, and satisfaction. Focus on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (quality and portion awareness.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Is olive oil really that important?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Yes! Extra virgin olive oil is rich in polyphenols with powerful anti-inflammatory) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (effects. Use it generously as your primary cooking and dressing oil. Choose high-quality,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.4 Td (cold-pressed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 532.6 Td (Q: Can I follow this diet on a budget?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (Absolutely. Beans, lentils, seasonal vegetables, whole grains, and eggs are affordable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 502.6 Td (staples. Buy olive oil in bulk. Canned fish is budget-friendly. Skip expensive specialty) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 488.6 Td (items.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 460.8 Td (Q: Do I need to drink wine?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (No. Wine is optional and not required for health benefits. If you don't drink, don't) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (start. The diet's benefits come primarily from the food pattern.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 403.0 Td (Q: How is this different from other healthy diets?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (The Mediterranean diet emphasizes healthy fats \(olive oil, fish\), moderate dairy, and the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (social aspect of eating. It's less restrictive than many diets and more sustainable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.0 Td (long-term.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 331.2 Td (Q: Can I eat bread?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (Yes! Whole grain bread is part of the Mediterranean diet. Choose sourdough, whole wheat,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.2 Td (or traditional rustic breads. Enjoy with olive oil instead of butter.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 273.4 Td (Q: What about dairy?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257.4 Td (Moderate dairy is included - primarily yogurt and cheese rather than milk. Choose) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 243.4 Td (fermented options when possible. If dairy-free, focus on other calcium sources.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 215.6 Td (Q: How quickly will I see health improvements?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 199.6 Td (Many people notice improved energy and digestion within 1-2 weeks. Blood markers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185.6 Td (\(cholesterol, inflammation\) may improve within 4-8 weeks of consistent adherence.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
